1
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,080
I plan

2
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:12,320
to go back to Quanzhou

3
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:13,840
to visit

4
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:15,080
Bai Mei's parents.

5
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,920
I invited you two here today

6
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:21,000
to thank you for your help.

7
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:23,480
Master Lin,

8
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:25,800
the dead are gone,

9
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,200
the living must move on.

10
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,160
On this trip to Quanzhou,

11
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,520
please take good care of yourself.

12
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:31,200
Yes.

13
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,560
I think Madam Bai's spirit in heaven

14
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,160
wouldn't want to see you

15
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,160
so depressed.

16
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,280
Father,

17
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:20,000
Mother,

18
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:21,560
I came back this time

19
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,280
just to bring Bai Mei's

20
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,280
favorite costume

21
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,160
to give to you.

22
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,440
Just treat it as if

23
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:27,720
she's staying by your side.

24
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,200
Guoying,

25
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,360
you're so thoughtful.

26
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,440
What did you just call me?

27
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:40,000
In our Quanzhou dialect,

28
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:41,720
"Rong"

29
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,160
is pronounced "Ying."

30
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,440
Your mother speaks

31
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:45,640
with a heavy accent.

32
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,200
Please don't mind her.

33
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:51,560
Brother Ying,

34
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,000
why

35
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,200
aren't you wearing your wedding suit?

36
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:04,000
Why wear this red opera costume?

37
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:06,360
Today is our big day.

38
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,640
This dress means a lot to us.

39
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,000
So,

40
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,920
I wanted to wear it with my husband

41
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:12,640
to spend this night together.

42
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,400
So that night,

43
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:46,360
the Brother Ying she called was me.

44
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:04,200
Bai Mei is so pitiful.

45
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,240
She loved Lin Guorong so deeply,

46
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,800
but ended up with

47
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,040
such a tragic fate.

48
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:11,040
All her deep affection

49
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:12,800
was given to the wrong person.

50
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:13,800
You men

51
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,080
are all no good.

52
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,640
Actually, back then,

53
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:23,920
on our wedding day,

54
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,800
I left suddenly

55
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,080
because I had no choice.

56
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,920
What do you mean no choice?

57
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:33,040
What could make you leave suddenly at that time?

58
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,520
Forget it.

59
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,480
Huang Jinrong,

60
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:50,040
we grew up as childhood sweethearts.

61
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,600
What on earth is it

62
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,520
that you can't tell me?

63
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:03,680
Fine.

64
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,400
You don't want to say it, right?

65
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,640
Then don't say it.

66
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:11,040
Never say it.

67
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,920
No wonder my Master said not to marry you.

68
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,120
Watch the blade!

69
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:03,760
Brother Bao!

70
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:04,680
Brother Bao!

71
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,320
Brother Bao!

72
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:09,760
Brother Bao!

73
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:10,880
Brother Bao, what's wrong?

74
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,080
Boss Mei,

75
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,760
what happened here?

76
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:15,440
I don't know either.

77
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,640
He was fine on stage this morning.

78
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,320
Suddenly he just...

79
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:19,880
Hurry!

80
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,240
Take him to the hospital first!

81
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:22,360
Right, right, right.

82
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:23,800
Uncle Qin,

83
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,640
hurry and take Brother Bao to the hospital!

84
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:29,760
Boss Mei,

85
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,080
I've already arranged for someone

86
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,520
to take Brother Bao to the hospital.

87
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:33,640
Good.

88
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:41,120
Why is it that once Senior Sister makes a comeback,

89
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:43,360
such a huge mess occurs?

90
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,760
Why are you back?

91
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,880
I had to come back.

92
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,320
Senior Sister, you are born under an unlucky star.

93
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:51,920
You have bad luck.

94
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,440
If I didn't come back,

95
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:54,680
this Opera House

96
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,520
probably wouldn't last much longer.

97
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:57,560
This Opera House

98
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,680
really won't last much longer, will it?

99
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,560
I don't know.

100
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,360
What nonsense are you talking about?

101
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,120
Why wouldn't the Opera House last?

102
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,560
Boss Mei

103
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,800
is a star performer in the opera world.

104
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,680
She's a genius.

105
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,240
What do you guys know?

106
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:10,560
Fine.

107
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,440
Then I'll see how you handle this.

108
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:14,880
Xiao Chun,

109
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,680
get my room ready.

110
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:21,440
Uncle Qin,

111
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,000
I think it's best

112
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,880
if you come with me to the hospital.

113
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,360
Let's go check on Brother Bao.

114
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:27,360
Okay, okay.

115
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:27,880
Boss Mei,

116
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,120
how about

117
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,440
I accompany you to the hospital?

118
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:31,760
Uncle Qin,

119
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,320
I must trouble you to make a trip

120
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:34,680
to the Police Department

121
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,080
and invite Inspector Huang over.

122
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,120
Okay.

123
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:38,320
Uncle Qin,

124
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,560
don't tell him

125
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,560
that I asked you to invite him.

126
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:41,760
Okay.

127
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:46,680
Boss Mei

128
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,120
The Inspector is here.

129
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:50,680
Duan Qingqing.

130
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,000
Why are you here?

131
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:54,880
Inspector Huang.

132
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,760
Today, Brother Bao was on stage,

133
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:57,920
and suddenly started foaming at the mouth.

134
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,000
He lost consciousness.

135
00:07:59,360 --> 00:07:59,880
Right now,

136
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,120
he's still in the emergency room.

137
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,120
Foaming at the mouth?

138
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,800
Did he eat something?

139
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,200
Doctor,

140
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:10,520
how is Brother Bao?

141
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,120
The patient has food poisoning.

142
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,000
We have already pumped

143
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,880
the patient's stomach.

144
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,240
His condition is basically stable now,

145
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,640
but he needs to stay for observation for a few days.

146
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,640
Do you know

147
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,520
what kind of food

148
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,320
caused the poisoning?

149
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,000
It's still unclear at the moment.

150
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,440
We have sent the patient's vomit

151
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,120
to the lab for testing.

152
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:24,760
For the specifics,

153
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,920
we'll have to wait for the test results.

154
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,240
You should go and handle

155
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,080
the admission procedures for the patient first.

156
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,320
Uncle Qin,

157
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,920
hurry and help Brother Bao

158
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,000
with the admission procedures.

159
00:08:36,680 --> 00:08:37,200
Boss Mei,

160
00:08:37,680 --> 00:08:38,760
before Brother Bao went on stage,

161
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,240
did he eat anything?

162
00:08:41,800 --> 00:08:43,120
I didn't see him eat anything.

163
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,200
It's just that before going on stage,

164
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:47,760
he drank a cup of my tea.

165
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:52,560
Boss Mei,

166
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,080
the one who just cursed the opera house to shut down,

167
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:55,680
that girl,

168
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,360
is she Xiao Yuejiao?

169
00:08:58,760 --> 00:08:59,320
Yes.

170
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:01,920
She is my Junior Sister,

171
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,640
and also the daughter of my Master,

172
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:05,680
the former boss of Hongfu Opera House.

173
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,320
Xiao Yuejiao.

174
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:11,360
I have previously

175
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,520
heard of this Xiao Yuejiao.

176
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,880
Hasn't she been out of town to join a troupe?

177
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,000
I don't know what happened,

178
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,120
but she suddenly came back.

179
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:20,920
I heard about it too.

180
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:23,320
They say that in the outside troupes,

181
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:25,000
her box office has never been very good.

182
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,320
Perhaps

183
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,800
this is the main reason

184
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:28,760
why she suddenly came back.

185
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:31,920
Then tell me,

186
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:33,640
this Xiao Yuejiao,

187
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,320
saying Boss Mei is born under an unlucky star,

188
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:36,880
and saying that her opera house

189
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:37,880
is about to close down,

190
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:39,040
is it...

191
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,360
Maybe

192
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,160
maybe it's because she wants to steal

193
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,240
Boss Mei's position.

194
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,360
But honestly,

195
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:54,760
if this time

196
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,360
Boss Mei is really forced out

197
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,240
and can never perform again,

198
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,640
then this Opera House

199
00:09:59,120 --> 00:09:59,840
might have to be given to

200
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,880
Xiao Yuejiao to take over.

201
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:02,760
That's right.

202
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:04,880
Judging from the current situation,

203
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,400
this Xiao Yuejiao

204
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:08,720
indeed has a strong motive.

205
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:10,280
Perhaps

206
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:12,120
the cup of tea Brother Bao drank

207
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:13,520
was what she intended to use

208
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,360
to poison Mei Yanhong.

209
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:15,840
It's just that

210
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:17,400
Brother Bao drank it by mistake.

211
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:18,880
But right now,

212
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,760
I don't have concrete evidence yet.

213
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,360
Then...

214
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:24,600
Then what are you going to do next?

215
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,720
I plan to investigate Xiao Yuejiao's

216
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,160
history of joining troupes out of town,

217
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:29,960
as well as the real purpose

218
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:30,760
of her return this time.

219
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,760
Only then can I determine

220
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,760
whether she is truly

221
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:33,760
unrelated to this case.

222
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:35,640
All right then.

223
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,520
So that we can continue

224
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,480
to hear Boss Mei's opera in the future,

225
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,280
for this investigation,

226
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,720
I'll join you.

227
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,120
If there's anything,

228
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,240
just tell me directly.

229
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,520
As for matters outside the case,

230
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:52,240
whenever you figure it out,

231
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,600
you can tell me then.

232
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,880
Our great Inspector...

233
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:03,720
Why haven't you smoothed things over with her yet?
